<P>
Photo, Brian Wilson declares charges by his cousin "out of the ballpark." ; 
Photo, Stan Love, right, with attorney Thomas M. Monson, wants psychological 
and psychiatric evaluations of Brian Wilson to be ordered. MARIANNA DIAMOS / 
For The Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
