REGIONAL EARNINGS: FLAMEMASTER CORP. PROFIT DOUBLES IN 2ND QUARTER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Flamemaster Corp. said its fiscal second-quarter profit more than doubled from 
a year earlier, to $228,975 from $97,217. 
</P>
<P>
The Sun Valley maker of coatings and sealants said the higher earnings came on 
a 44% gain in its revenue, to $1.56 million from $1.08 million. Flamemaster 
attributed the gains to improved production and packaging techniques and to a 
broader line of products. 
</P>
<P>
For the first half of its fiscal year, Flamemaster's profit jumped to $339,010 
from $123,210, and its six-month revenue rose to $2.67 million from $1.66 
million. 
