<TEXT>
<P>
Federal Home Loan Mortgage Corp.: Reston, Va.-based Freddie Mac reported a 
first-quarter profit of $111 million, up 7% from the same period last year. The 
Congressionally chartered corporation credited growth in its total mortgage 
portfolio. 
