<P>
PROPOSITION 108 (MASS TRANSIT BOND); PROPOSITION 111 (GASOLINE TAX); TELEVISION 
ADVERTISING; POLITICAL ADVERTISING; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; CALIFORNIA 
-- TRANSPORTATION; TRANSPORTATION ROUTES; TRAFFIC MANAGEMENT 
</P>
