form came off without a hitch over the weekend, when the Momix dance troupe 
performed partially nude at Saddleback College. . . . As is customary when the 
college knows about nudity, notices were included in the series brochure and 
mailed with tickets. . . . The performances were well received and there were 
no complaints or ticket returns. Mark I. Pinsky and David Reyes 
