<TEXT>
<P>
Coach Dan DeLeon of El Toro High School has named La Quinta's Dave Demarest and 
Fountain Valley's Ron LaRuffa as his assistants for the South team in the 
Orange County All-Star baseball game June 12 at Glover Stadium in Anaheim. 
</P>
